    description: 'Master the methods used to collect topographic data in the field, including radial, grid, and cross-section methods. Learn professional field documentation practices including field book procedures, electronic data collection, and raw data file management. These skills are tested directly on the FS exam.',
    estimatedMinutes: 20,
